# Golden Test Cases

This folder contains benchmark scenarios used to evaluate the reasoning quality of the AI Product Assistant.

Each test case includes:

- Requirement
- Customer Problem
- Customer Value
- Hypothesis
- Recommended Vertical Slice
- Alternative Solution
- Trade-off
- SPIDR Pattern
- INVEST Review
- Build Later
- Questions for Product Owner

The purpose of these test cases is to ensure the AI provides consistent reasoning rather than simply generating User Stories.
